legal-ai-copilot/
├── backend/                     # The Python FastAPI Backend
│   ├── services/                # Logic modules (The "Brain")
│   │   ├── ai_engine.py         # Handles Gemini API prompts & parsing
│   │   └── pdf_utils.py         # Handles extracting text from PDF uploads
│   ├── config.py                # Settings & Environment variables (API Keys)
│   ├── main.py                  # API Entry point (Routes: /analyze, etc.)
│   ├── models.py                # Pydantic models (Data validation schemas)
│   └── requirements.txt         # Python dependencies
│
├── frontend/                    # The React Frontend
│   ├── src/
│   │   └── App.jsx              # The main UI (Chat + Analysis Dashboard)
│   ├── public/
│   └── package.json             # JS dependencies (React, Tailwind, Lucide)
│
└── .env                         # Local secrets file (Stores GEMINI_API_KEY)